name: MultiCare Surgical Products
overview:
Incorporated at New Delhi, India, we “MultiCare Surgical Products Corporation”, is an ISO 9001:2008

Products: Latex Examination Gloves (CE) Examination Gloves Sterile Gloves Surgical Gloves Latex Sterile Surgical Gloves (ISO, ISI, CE) Powdered Surgical Gloves Latex Non Sterile Surgical Gloves (ISO, ISI, CE) Disposable Plastics Gloves

Mission: We are committed to the Care and improvement of human life. In recognition of this commitment, we strive to deliver high quality, cost effective healthcare in the communities we serve.

Clientele: We are delighted to say that 75% of our entire product range is being exported regularly. The products offered by us are manufactured in complete compliance with set market standards.

Our Team Of Experts: We have a team of highly skilled work force, an energetic, creative merchandising team & experienced technical professionals who blend perfectly to manufacture high quality products.
